questions.quote: I tell ya, I-, I'm gonna go read in my room for a little while.
You don't have to do that, I'll pay for myself. But just the fact that you want me to have fun with you guys - that's so sweet! Come here.
Ohh, sweetie! Hey, I bet you anything that he's gonna call you again.
Although, maybe just... one last moment of weakness... Goodbye Chandler Bing.
I just got a call to be a dancer on a television special for New Year's Eve. It's called some sort of Dick'n Rock'n Dickie Eve.
Somebody wanna help me, tryin' to rip out my heart. Uh, that's great. Anybody seen a nipple?
Yeah but see I have nothing to compare it too. So even if you're horrible, how would I know?
Come on, you saw the way he ran out of here! What do you think? He's gonna stick around and talk to the daughter he abandoned!
Laugh all you want but uh, she actually left me a message saying she'd like to go out again.
Well, I see you've had a very productive day. Don't you think the cowboy hat is a little much?
